        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Guarding against Unexploded Arms and Munitions Act or the GUAM Act</strong></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of Defense (DOD) to use amounts available for operation and maintenance to remove munitions and explosives of concern from military installations in Guam.</p> <p>DOD must monitor and assess such removal and constantly update the processes for removal to mitigate any issues.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
